{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"59f569cbef","title":"中共中央、国务院、中央军委、中央文革关于纪念今年“五一”国际劳动节的通知","origin":"根据湖北省革命委员会编印《无产阶级文化大革命文件汇编[三]》，武汉：1969年3月","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2a846198f8","index":0,"year":1968,"month":4,"day":24,"articleId":"59f569cbef"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3457e40c94","name":"党内资产阶级","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"ef71f03227","name":"中央文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"857aaa58b1","type":"title","text":"中共中央、国务院、中央军委、中央文革关于纪念今年“五一”国际劳动节的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"59f569cbef"},{"id":"21e4938504","type":"paragraph","text":"一、一九六八年的“五一”国际劳动节的庆祝活动，仍照过去规定，采取分散纪念的办法，不搞全市性的大型集体游行。各地可在市内工厂、学校、机关、部队、街道各单位分别举行小型的庆祝集会。","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"59f569cbef"},{"id":"89b0ddca09","type":"paragraph","text":"二、今年“五一”节，一概不邀请外宾参加活动。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"59f569cbef"},{"id":"77e5a66281","type":"paragraph","text":"三、加强敌情观念，提高革命警惕性。国防前线要特别加强警戒，城市要加强治安管理工作厂矿、企业、机关、学校要加强内部的安全保卫，严防叛徒、特务、顽固不化的走资派和地、富、反、坏、右分子的破坏活动。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"59f569cbef"},{"id":"a20d039657","type":"paragraph","text":" 一九六八年四月二十四日","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"59f569cbef"},{"id":"3d5abb8d35","type":"paragraph","text":"附一九六八年纪念“五一”国际劳动节标语口号。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"59f569cbef"},{"id":"4e2829d2bd","type":"subtitle","text":"纪念“五一”国际劳动节标语口号","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"59f569cbef"},{"id":"e8cfda95e3","type":"paragraph","text":"１、庆祝“五一”国际劳动节！","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"59f569cbef"},{"id":"1d89cd2e06","type":"paragraph","text":"２、全世界无产者联合起来！全世界无产者同被压迫人民、被压迫民族联合起来！","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"59f569cbef"},{"id":"8e83107844","type":"paragraph","text":"３、打倒以美国为首的帝国主义！","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"59f569cbef"},{"id":"30d4a55c42","type":"paragraph","text":"４、打倒以苏修领导集团为中心的现代修正主义！","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"59f569cbef"},{"id":"d6bcb1cba6","type":"paragraph","text":"５、打倒各国反动派！","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"59f569cbef"},{"id":"30ef117b63","type":"paragraph","text":"６、坚决支持越南人民的抗美救国战争！","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"59f569cbef"},{"id":"9c289ed846","type":"paragraph","text":"７、坚决支持美国黑人抗暴斗争！","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"59f569cbef"},{"id":"c25ab4a702","type":"paragraph","text":"８、坚决支持各国人民的革命斗争！","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"59f569cbef"},{"id":"17c6ca6770","type":"paragraph","text":"９、向各国的马克思列宁主义政党和团体致敬！坚决支持全世界马克思列宁主义者的反帝反修斗争！","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"59f569cbef"},{"id":"8cea72151e","type":"paragraph","text":"１０、无产阶级专政万岁！","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"59f569cbef"},{"id":"25a07fe456","type":"paragraph","text":"１１、无产阶级文化大革命的全面胜利万岁！","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"59f569cbef"},{"id":"14c25f9890","type":"paragraph","text":"１２、毛主席的无产阶级革命路线胜利万岁！","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"59f569cbef"},{"id":"a2daf44ae2","type":"paragraph","text":"１３、高举毛泽东思想伟大红旗，把无产阶级文化大革命进行到底！","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"59f569cbef"},{"id":"aadb17426e","type":"paragraph","text":"１４、打倒卖国贼蒋介石！解放台湾！","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"59f569cbef"},{"id":"23b56e8d96","type":"paragraph","text":"１５、向无产阶级革命派致敬！向工人、贫、下中农和革命的红卫兵小将致敬！","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"59f569cbef"},{"id":"f041fd98fd","type":"paragraph","text":"１６、向伟大的中国人民解放军学习！向伟大的中国人民解放军致敬！","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"59f569cbef"},{"id":"c7d75d4ee5","type":"paragraph","text":"１７、英雄的中国人民万岁！","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"59f569c